responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "1FC1F4F448365E034A3ED994805FFDA7", "To my dear little Jennah, Your mother would have loved to have played in the river with us. She couldn\'t swim, of course, but she still loved the water just like you. The rivers here are cold and refreshing, and the water is clear as air. On days like this, I\'m reminded of how we spent your childhood.")
